					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Nothing seems wrong, but it's very probable that most emulators still behave like there is 4 different switch registers, so write to $8000 will partially write to the $8000 registers instead of simply queuing for the final write like the real MMC1 behave.
<br />Try to make all writes to the same adress.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Life is complex: it has both real and imaginary components.</div>
